web --><div class="bc-tray bc-action-sheet mosaic-action-sheet bc-action-sheet-dimmer bc-color-background-base" role="dialog" aria-label="By:" id="authors-action-sheet"><div class="tray-wrapper"><div class="tray-content"><span><ul class="bc-list bc-spacing-s1 bc-spacing-top-s1 bc-list-nostyle"><li class="bc-list-item mosaic-action-sheet-label bc-pub-centered-container" id="authors-action-sheet-label"><div class="bc-box bc-box-padding-base"><span class="bc-text bc-size-title2">By:</span></div></li><li class="bc-list-item bc-action-sheet-item mosaic-action-sheet-item"><a class="bc-link bc-color-base" tabindex="0" href="/search?searchAuthor=Evan+M.+Calderon&ref_pageloadid=3Qw7jonbCiATsAp7&pf_rd_p=f6da0b63-439d-48a7-a859-b187b7c50705&pf_rd_r=EB1AB399WPCCVYCMJ4EY&plink=q63tyR1YAPHPvk84&pageLoadId=0Y1F6QDLhLxoPxUq&creativeId=16015ba4-2e2d-4ae3-93c5-e937781a25cd&ref=a_pd_PLC-Pr_c1_author_1"><div class="bc-box bc-box-padding-s2"><span class="bc-text bc-size-title2"><span class="mosaic-action-sheet-item-text">Evan M. Calderon</span></span></div></a></li></ul></span></div></div><div class="tray-fixed bc-box-padding-s2 bc-spacing-top-minus-s2"><span data-trigger="authors-action-sheet" class="bc-trigger bc-core-actionsheet-cancel bc-pub-block bc-trigger-actionsheet"><span class="bc-button bc-button-outline"><button class="bc-button-text" type="button" tabindex="0"><span class="bc-text bc-button-text-inner bc-size-action-large"><span class="bc-text bc-size-title2">Close</span></span></button></span></span></div></div></div><div id="virtual-voice-banner" class="slot centerSlot"></div><div id="promo-banner" class="slot centerSlot"></div><div id="center-1-1" class="slot centerSlot"><link rel="stylesheet" href="https://m.media-amazon.com/images/I/01nB9Ffu7mL.css?AUIClients/AudibleLegoWidgetsAssets"><link rel="stylesheet" href="https://m.media-amazon.com/images/I/215XsPC5kwL.css?AUIClients/AudibleProductContentAssets"><link rel="stylesheet" href="https://m.media-amazon.com/images/I/017c-E3u2tL._RC|01BVRyXJHhL.css,21BNpZEaA8L.css_.css?AUIClients/AudibleBuyBoxAssets"><link rel="stylesheet" href="https://m.media-amazon.com/images/I/01PIy4uOPtL.css?AUIClients/AudibleWebSearchAssets"><link rel="stylesheet" href="https://m.media-amazon.com/images/I/01RWLidK0lL.css?AUIClients/AudibleDailyDealsAssets"><link rel="stylesheet" href="https://m.media-amazon.com/images/I/01sh+SxRLIL.css?AUIClients/AudibleReviewsAssets"><link rel="stylesheet" href="https://m.media-amazon.com/images/I/31TJV3HflCL.css?AUIClients/AudibleWebCarouselAssets"><link rel="stylesheet" href="https://m.media-amazon.com/images/I/31vVYXmaY+L.css?AUIClients/AudibleWebAddressAndPaymentsAssets"><link rel="stylesheet" href="https://m.media-amazon.com/images/I/012TDX1mv5L.css?AUIClients/AudibleWebNotificationAssets"><div id="membership-c11-widget" class="bc-box bc-spacing-medium bc-palette-default"><div class="bc-box-padding-none bc-color-secondary bc-pub-clearfix" style="background: #ffffff"><div class="dlp-hero"><div class="dlp-hero-contain"><div class="hero-img" style="height:"><img id="" class="js-only-element" src="https://m.media-amazon.com/images/G/30/AudibleES/es_ES/adbl_web/PDPs/background-tts-es.png" alt="Background images"></div><div class="hero-content full-height"><div id="" class="bc-row bc-container dlp-v-center bc-spacing-top-none bc-color-base" style=""><div class="bc-col bc-text-center bc-col-12"><div id="" class="bc-row bc-spacing-none" style=""><h2 class="bc-heading bc-color-base bc-size-medium bc-text-bold">This title uses virtual voice narration</h2><div id="" class="bc-row bc-spacing-top-micro" style=""><span class="bc-text bc-size-base bc-color-secondary">Virtual voice is computer-generated narration for audiobooks.</span></div></div><div id="" class="bc-row bc-spacing-top-micro" style=""><span class="bc-text bc-size-mini bc-color-secondary"></span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div id="center-1-2" class="slot centerSlot"><adbl-style-scope class="adjusted-grid-layout"><adbl-product-details class="product-details-widget-spacing"><adbl-text-block slot="summary"><p><b>Master PLC Programming and Industrial Automation with Real-World Examples</b></p><p>From manufacturing plants and conveyor systems to HVAC control and smart packaging lines, <b>Programmable Logic Controllers (PLCs)</b> are the backbone of modern automation. This comprehensive guide takes you step by step from PLC basics to advanced applications, equipping you with the skills to design, program, and troubleshoot industrial systems.</p>What You’ll Learn Inside:<p>✅ <b>PLC Fundamentals</b> – Understand PLC hardware, inputs/outputs, communication, and software tools.<br>✅ <b>Programming Languages</b> – Learn Ladder Logic, Structured Text, and Function Block programming (IEC 61131-3 standard).<br>✅ <b>Timers, Counters, and Data Handling</b> – Build precise and reliable control sequences.<br>✅ <b>Analog I/O & HMI/SCADA Integration</b> – Work with sensors, actuators, and operator interfaces.<br>✅ <b>Safety, Interlocks & Error Handling</b> – Design safe, fail-proof control logic.<br>✅ <b>Advanced Topics</b> – Explore Industry 4.0, IoT integration, OPC UA, MQTT, edge computing, and predictive maintenance.<br>✅ <b>Case Studies</b> – Hands-on examples including conveyor belt control, traffic lights, tank level management, packaging/sorting, and HVAC automation.</p>Why This Book?<ul><li><p>Covers <b>popular brands</b>: Siemens, Allen-Bradley, and Schneider.</p></li><li><p>Written in a <b>clear, practical style</b> with diagrams, ladder logic, and structured examples.</p></li><li><p>Includes <b>troubleshooting guides, coding standards, and quick references</b> for the field.</p></li><li><p>Bridges <b>theory and practice</b>, making it useful for beginners and working professionals alike.</p></li></ul><p>Whether you’re an <b>engineering student, technician, or automation professional</b>, this book will serve as your <b>complete reference and training manual</b> for PLC programming.</p><p>Take control of automation today — and prepare for the future of smart factories, Industry 4.0, and AI-driven industrial systems.</p></adbl-text-block><adbl-product-metadata slot="metadata" class="product-metadata" interactive aria-label="Product details"><script type="application/json">{
